    <item>
      <title>Version 1.1.0</title>
      <pubDate>Tue, 15 Jul 2026 12:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>2</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>1.1.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>14.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[
        <h2>v1.1.0 — Pinch to Brightness</h2>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Pinch gesture</strong> — spread to increase brightness, pinch to decrease (built-in + external displays via DDC)</li>
          <li><strong>Sparkle auto-updater</strong> — Check for Updates in the menu bar, daily background checks</li>
          <li>Pinch on/off toggle and target (brightness or volume) in Settings → Gestures</li>
          <li>Settings → General: auto-update toggle</li>
        </ul>
      ]]></description>
